Pascaline Crêvecoeur https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pascaline_Cr%C3%AAvecoeur 0 Pascaline Crêvecoeur (born 30 April 1982) is a French-speaking actress in both cinema and theatre. She graduated from Insas, National Institute of Performing Arts - Brussels/Belgium, in 2007. Pascaline_Crêvecoeur ( born 30_April_1982 ) is a_French-speaking_actress in both_cinema_and_theatre . She graduated from Insas , National_Institute of Performing Arts - Brussels/Belgium , in 2007 .
